Question: One image shows a spaniel in a Santa hat gazing leftward at a tree.

Right image URL: https://i.pinimg.com/736x/02/01/df/0201df5fc2835973b2dd0c46f869b404--christmas-friends-christmas-dog.jpg

Program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is there a spaniel in a Santa hat gazing leftward at a tree?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is there a spaniel in a Santa hat gazing leftward at a tree?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} xor {ANSWER1}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
